text:
Phew～......!
We really pushed ourselves, huh～......!

I'm like, super hungy～! I was thinking, 
once we finished we should go grab a late dinner～
So, Fuyuko-chan, want to eat something!?
You... at this time of night...

Yo, they've got "Hamburg Steak"!
──Ah, theres also an Okonomiyaki shop!?

Now listen, there's no way we're eating 
somehting that heavy at this hour──

......Hamburg Steak!
If you're going to eat, might as well go all in.

You know it～!
I'll have this then～!
